ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of RORY CAMPBELL of Edmonton, Alberta, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Robert McLeod, who term has expired.
